      {
        "name": "PostgreSQL (Primary + Sync Replica)",
        "responsibility": "Source of truth for courier assignments and availability. Uses row-level locking (SELECT FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED) to prevent double-assignment. Synchronous replication to one replica ensures zero data loss on failover.",
