    {
      "risk": "Operational burden exceeds 2-person team capacity",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "Use managed services wherever possible (managed PostgreSQL, managed message queue). Keep the architecture to a single deployable service. Avoid microservice decomposition. Invest in observability (structured logging, key metrics dashboard) early."
