      "recommendation": "Option A (CP). The cost of a 5-15 second assignment delay during rare DB failover events is vastly lower than the operational complexity of conflict resolution. For a 2-person team, simplicity is a survival requirement. Double-assignment has real-world consequences (two couriers showing up, customer confusion, wasted courier time) that outweigh brief delays."
